; The eslint@10 + eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y@6.10 pairing has a known peer-dep
; mismatch — jsx-a11y's peer caps at eslint 9. A full upgrade to
; eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y@7+ is a separate repo-wide task (see the
; hardening report IK-following the known-limitations note). Until then,
; npm must fall through to legacy peer resolution so both Vercel and
; local installs succeed without --force.
legacy-peer-deps=true
